OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FOther cast members include Pippa
OL,7,FHaywood, Robert Gilbert, Sasha Behar
OL,8,Fand Celine Arden.
OL,10,FITV News understands that Colm
OL,11,FMcCarthy will direct the show - he has
OL,12,Fheaded up episodes for a number of BBC
OL,13,Fhits such as Spooks, Sherlock, Doctor
OL,14,FWho and Peaky Blinders.
OL,16,FExecutive Producer Toby Whithouse also
OL,17,Fspoke exclusively to ITV News, sharing
OL,18,Fhis hope to "keep Jersey at the
OL,19,Fabsolute heart of the show" and to
OL,20,Fbuild up the island's filming
OL,21,Finfrastructure for future series.
