OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FUnlike the original which tackled a
OL,7,Fnew storyline for each episode, the
OL,8,Fremake will see one mystery run across
OL,9,Fthe series.
OL,11,FShowmakers want to honour Bergerac's
OL,12,Fhistory with a contemporary twist and
OL,13,Fsay viewers will be reintroduced to
OL,14,Fhim as a broken man, dealing with
OL,15,Fgrief and alcoholism after his wife's
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,FWhen a woman from a rich Jersey family
OL,19,Fis murdered, Jim must deal with his
OL,20,Fpersonal struggles as he tries to
OL,21,Fcrack the case.
