OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FThe island's tourist board Visit
OL,7,FJersey has put its support behind the
OL,8,Frebooted show, with Chief Executive
OL,9,FTricia Warwick saying: "For many, the
OL,10,Fwords 'Jersey' and 'Bergerac' are
OL,11,Fsynonymous and we are delighted for
OL,12,Fthe iconic TV series to return to our
OL,13,Fisland's beautiful shores.
OL,15,F"The modern re-imaging presents an
OL,16,Fopportunity to celebrate the show's
OL,17,Flegacy in Jersey, whilst reaching a
OL,18,Fnew generation of fans who will be
OL,19,Feager to 'jet set' to the featured
OL,20,Flocations."
