OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FFilming is due to begin in July and
OL,7,Fwill include locations in Jersey and
OL,8,Fthe UK.
OL,10,FThe show will air across six episodes
OL,11,Ffor free on UKTV channel U&DRAMA and
OL,12,Fonline streaming service U in 2025.
